divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing in my front yard and i saw it come from behind the trees, it crossed over my street and made kind of a loop and went over my house it was very low i did get a picture of it. i know it was not a star. after it passed over my house it floated out my view point, i was puzzled, amazed and i really don't feel like myself anymore. I know for a fact that we are not alone. There is something out there.
